&lt;p&gt;Navigating student loans can feel overwhelming, but understanding your options is crucial for your financial future. This comprehensive guide covers everything from federal vs. private loans to repayment strategies and forgiveness programs for 2025.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Student Loan Landscape in 2025 
